Rattrap:




Rattrap watched as the hatch of the pod opened, but nothing came out 
the way it suppose to. He pinned his ears to the side and leaned up 
to the side of the pod and looked inside. A female layed inside of it 
unconscious. 

He looked around, then back to Squizzy. "I could never get these 
things. Why can't dis one pop open like they supposed ta?" He sighed.
